    "asOf": "2025-01-16",
    "date": "2025-04-07T14:02:11Z",
    "text": "Protecting Homeowners from Disaster Act of 2025 \n\nThis bill repeals the limit on the itemized tax deduction for unreimbursed personal casualty losses. Specifically, the bill repeals a provision that generally limits the deduction for tax years 2018-2025 to losses that are attributable to a federally declared disaster. The bill applies to losses sustained after 2024.\u00a0"
